    "body": "Possible script (for Mac)\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3.6 -m venv vyper-env\r\nsource vyper-env/bin/activate\r\npip install vyper\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf a `requirements.txt` exists\r\n\r\n```\r\npython3.6 -m venv vyper-env\r\nsource vyper-env/bin/activate\r\npip install -r requirements.txt\r\n```",
